15 WHEREAS, Hope Atlanta has expanded its impact by merging hunger relief with housing
16 solutions, integrating mental health services, and championing long-term stability for those
17 in crisis; and
18 WHEREAS, during Hope Atlanta's distinguished history, the organization has changed lives
19 by assisting people in our community with finding permanent housing, reuniting families,
20 and helping individuals avoid evictions; and
21 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable organization be
22 appropriately honored during this special time.
23 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
24 the members of this body commend Hope Atlanta's unwavering commitment to dignity,
25 stability, and opportunity for all; celebrate its enduring mission to end homelessness in our
26 community; and extend the most sincere congratulations upon the grand occasion of its 125th
27 anniversary.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Hope
30 Atlanta.
